#define WrestleWin ["Your struggle is akin to a moth fluttering against the sun, %s. Peace now.","I sense no malice in you, only confusion. Allow me to bring clarity to this conflict, %s.","The cosmic balance remains undisturbed by your efforts, %s. Go in peace.","Why invite a confrontation you were never destined to win? Be still, %s.","Your energy is faint. Seek not the path of conflict, for you are not yet prepared, %s.","You possess a flickering light, %s. Do not waste it in a futile crusade.","I have witnessed the birth of galaxies; your resistance is merely a fleeting moment, %s.","There is no equilibrium in your current approach, %s. Learn and grow.","It is not in my nature to destroy, yet I cannot allow your disruption, %s.","May you find the wisdom to understand why this was necessary, %s.","You fight with purpose, %s, but you lack the foresight to see its futility.","Balance has been restored. Your part in this play is finished, %s.","You are an interesting soul, %s. Do not let this defeat define your journey.","Your strength is significant, but it is not aligned with the cosmic order, %s.","We are all bound by destiny. Today, your path led to this outcome, %s.","A commendable clash, %s. You demonstrate a strength that warrants respect.","I feel the echoes of your struggle. It resonates with the complexity of life, %s.","You are quite adept, %s. If only you focused that energy toward creation.","It brings me no joy to subdue a warrior of such conviction, %s.","The tide turns, as all things must. You have done well, %s.","You are truly a remarkable entity, %s. Rarely do I encounter one who pushes me thus.","Your essence is vibrant and strong, %s. You are a noteworthy ripple in the cosmic stream.","I have tested your limits, %s, and found them to be of extraordinary depth.","Such passion... it is both a gift and a burden. You have fought magnificently, %s.","This duel shall remain etched in my memory. You are a formidable soul, %s.","We are echoes of the same cosmic harmony, %s! Your power rivals the stars themselves.","To stand against me is a heavy burden, and you have borne it with grace, %s.","I sense a great destiny in your path, %s. Today, our paths diverged in violence, but not in honor.","You are a warrior of immense spirit, %s. It was a clash of titans indeed.","The balance was thin between us, %s. You are a true peer in power.","Finally, a soul that challenges the very silence of the void! Magnificent, %s.","You occupy a unique space in the tapestry of existence, %s. An encounter I shall treasure.","Your power is a testament to the chaos and beauty of the universe, %s.","We are matched in essence and might. The stars themselves watched us today, %s.","You are a guardian of your own destiny, %s. It was a privilege to witness such greatness."]

#define WrestleDefeat ["I... I sense a shift in the cosmic design. You are far more than you appear, %s.","My logic failed to account for your hidden depths. A profound lesson, %s.","The universe is full of mysteries. You are the greatest of them today, %s.","I am humbled. You have revealed a truth I had yet to perceive, %s.","Perhaps my perspective was clouded. You have opened my eyes, %s.","You are a catalyst for change, %s. I shall study your influence.","My equilibrium has been disrupted. You possess a unique resonance, %s.","I yield, for my understanding of you was flawed, %s.","You fight not just with force, but with something I had not calculated, %s.","This outcome was not in the stars, yet it has come to pass. Remarkable, %s.","You have surpassed my expectations, %s. Your path is one of great significance.","I accept this outcome. You are a far greater challenge than I anticipated, %s.","The order of things has been challenged, and you have emerged the victor, %s.","My power is but a tool; you have found a way to blunt it, %s.","A fascinating variable has entered the equation. Well fought, %s.","You have achieved what few ever have, %s. Your spirit is immense.","I am bested. You carry a strength that commands the very fabric of reality, %s.","The cosmic flow has shifted. You have directed it, %s.","You fight with a clarity I did not expect. You have won this day, %s.","I yield. You are a warrior of undeniable prowess, %s.","Your resolve is equal to the stars, %s. I concede this duel with honor.","I feel the weight of your power. It is profound, %s.","You have outmatched the Guardian of the Soul. I am truly stunned, %s.","A victory of incredible magnitude. You are the architect of your own fate, %s.","You are a beacon in the cosmos. I have been bested by a great soul, %s.","We are truly peers in strength. This victory is yours, %s, and it is a massive one.","You have challenged the heavens and prevailed. A feat of unimaginable spirit, %s.","I have met my match. You are a power that the universe must surely acknowledge, %s.","A struggle of mythic proportions. You are triumphant, and I salute your resolve, %s.","You have mastered the balance. I have been overcome, %s.","You are the center of the cosmic convergence. You have conquered the unconquerable, %s.","Truly, you are an apex of existence. I stand in awe of your triumph, %s.","You have rewritten the prophecy. You are the guardian the universe awaits, %s.","A victory that shall reverberate through eternity. I bow to your might, %s.","You are the new harmony. It was an honor to fall to such a singular being, %s."]

